FLY: Racial flight for winged races

Syntax: fly [off|land]

Winged races (gargoyles, dragons in dragon form, faeries, etc.) can
take flight.
Does not auto-move rooms; use normal exits while airborne.
Type 'fly off' or 'fly land' to return to the ground.

Distinct from the Fly spell (cast fly).

SEE ALSO: breath, races, abilities
